<section condition="TITLE=Trade Middle Office: Secure Email" id="SE"
         role="TOPIC">
  <title>Secure Email</title>

  <para role="TEXT">This action and its sub-menu items allow the creation of a
  new record for Sending a secure Email. For transactions that are not in the
  <xi:include href="../entities_en.xml" xpointer="ent_appli"
  xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"/>, the Bank
  User/<glossterm>Administrator</glossterm> uses the Middle Office
  <emphasis>New Secure Email</emphasis> option to send advises and
  notifications to customers.<indexterm>
      <primary>Secure Email</primary>
    </indexterm></para>

  <section role="ITEM">
    <title>Secure Email - Navigation</title>

    <para role="TEXT">After selecting the <emphasis role="bold">Trade Middle
    Office</emphasis> option from the Administrator's list on the home page,
    the <emphasis role="bold">Secure Email</emphasis> function can be selected
    from the left side navigation menu.<indexterm>
        <primary>Secure Email</primary>

        <secondary>Navigation</secondary>
      </indexterm><indexterm>
        <primary>Navigation</primary>

        <secondary>Secure Email</secondary>
      </indexterm><graphic fileref="./images/BUG_MidOff_secure_nav.jpg"
    width="160mm"/></para>
  </section>

  <section role="ITEM">
    <title>Secure Email Options</title>

    <para role="TEXT">When the <emphasis role="bold">Secure Email</emphasis>
    function is selected from the side navigation menu of the Trade
    Administration module, a number of options are listed.</para>

    <para role="TEXT"><inlinegraphic align="center" contentwidth="50mm"
    fileref="./images/BUG_MidOff_secure_options.jpg" width="100mm"/></para>

    <para role="TEXT">The available options are:<indexterm>
        <primary>Options</primary>

        <secondary>Secure Email</secondary>
      </indexterm><indexterm>
        <primary>Secure Email</primary>

        <secondary>Options</secondary>
      </indexterm><variablelist role="TEXT">
        <varlistentry>
          <term><guimenuitem moreinfo="none">From Scratch</guimenuitem></term>

          <listitem>
            <para role="TEXT">Create a new Secure Email notification from a blank
            form.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>

        <varlistentry>
          <term><guimenuitem moreinfo="none">Edit
          Transactions</guimenuitem></term>

          <listitem>
            <para role="TEXT">Review, complete and submit Secure Email notifications that
            you or another user have already created and saved, but not yet
            submitted.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>

        <varlistentry>
          <term><guimenuitem moreinfo="none">Retrieve
          Unsigned</guimenuitem></term>

          <listitem>
            <para role="TEXT">Review and submit Secure Email notifications that you or
            another user have created but have not been submitted due to lack
            of authority.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
      </variablelist></para>
  </section>

  <section condition="TITLE=Secure Email: From Scratch;PERM:tradeadmin_se_access;ACCESS=SE_01"
           id="SE_Scratch" role="ITEM">
    <title>Secure Email - From Scratch</title>

    <para role="TEXT">Clicking the Secure Email <guisubmenu>From
    Scratch</guisubmenu> sub-menu item opens a form that allows the email
    details to be entered.</para>

    <para role="TEXT"><graphic fileref="./images/BUG_MidOff_secure_new.jpg"
    width="160mm"/>The input form has the following sections.<indexterm>
        <primary>Secure Email</primary>

        <secondary>New</secondary>
      </indexterm></para>

