    <section role="ITEM">
      <title>From Scratch Form - Action Buttons</title>

      <para role="TEXT">The operations that can be performed from this form
      are listed below. They appear at the top (and bottom) of each relevant
      web page. For each of them, a pop up window will appear to confirm the
      choice.</para>

      <informaltable role="TEXT">
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="2.0*"/>

          <colspec colname="c3" colwidth="6.0*"/>

          <thead>
            <row>
              <entry nameend="c2" namest="c1"
              valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Operation</para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Description</para></entry>
            </row>
          </thead>

          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry valign="middle"><para role="TEXT"> <guiicon
              moreinfo="none">Save</guiicon> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Save the transaction details
              (including the status, possible back-office reference, comment,
              and all the optional modifications of the transaction details)
              as a draft. The message remains as a pending record without
              being sent to the client. No validation of the mandatory fields
              is performed at this stage.</para></entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry valign="middle"><para role="TEXT"> <guiicon
              moreinfo="none">Submit</guiicon> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Send the message to the client. Do
              this when all the requested (and mandatory) transaction details
              have been entered and the resulting record is ready for
              submission. </para><para role="TEXT">Depending submitting users jurisdiction
              profile (in particular, the amount they are authorised to
              validate without an additional signature), the amendment is
              either sent to the client or remains in the bank workspace as
              unsigned. </para></entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry valign="middle"><para role="TEXT"> <guiicon
              moreinfo="none">Cancel</guiicon> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Leave the current page and return to
              the <xi:include href="../entities_en.xml"
              xpointer="ent_Trade_MO"
              xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"/> main
              menu.</para></entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry valign="middle"><para role="TEXT"> <guiicon
              moreinfo="none">Help</guiicon> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Open a pop up window displaying the
              online help pages.</para></entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </informaltable>
    </section>
